---
title: Cajun-Style Chicken and Peppers with Savoury Rice and Garlicky Mayo
description: Sweet and smoky Cajun flavours add a zesty spin to this easy dinner! Chicken and veggies are tossed on a sheet and popped in the oven, while you make green onion-studded rice. Easy to make and even easier to enjoy.
